                                             12


Elementary science standards are grouped by grade level, and each grade level is identified by an
icon.
Elementary science standards include the following content domains.
   •  Earth and Space Science (ESS)
   •  Life Science (LS)
   •  Physical Science (PS)
   •  Engineering & Technology (ET)
