 changes form, even in transitions in which it  address scientific and engineering questions and problems.     describe physical quantities such as mass,
 seems to vanish.                                                                                              length, temperature, and volume.
 PS1.B: Chemical Reactions
 -No matter what reaction or change in
 properties occurs, the total mass of the
 substances does not change.
