HS-PS3-2                                                                                                                               ND Science Standards
ENERGY
                Performance Standard                Develop and use models to illustrate that energy is associated with
                         HS-PS3-2                   motion and relative position of particles (objects).
 Clarification Statement                            Physical Science: Emphasis is on energy associated with the different states of matter.
                                                    Chemistry: Emphasis on phenomena relating to the Kinetic Molecular Theory in all phases of matter.
                                                    Possible models include diagrams, drawings, descriptions, and computer simulations.
                                                    Physics: Emphasis on phenomena relating to the Kinetic Molecular Theory in all phases of matter.
