Earth’s Systems
              Performance Standard        Develop a quantitative model to describe the cycling of carbon among the
                      HS-ESS2-6           hydrosphere, atmosphere, geosphere, and biosphere.
 Clarification Statement                  Earth Science/Environmental Science: Emphasis is on modeling biogeochemical cycles that include the
