  a
    describe* the situation people want to change in terms of a simple problem that can be solved with the development of a new or improved object or tool.
  Defining the features of the solution
4 With guidance, students describe* the desired features of the tool or object that would solve the problem, based on scientific information, materials available,
  a
    and potential related benefits to people and other living things.
