    i. The specific criterion or constraint to be used.
3 a ii. What is to be changed in each trial (the independent variable).
    iii. The outcome (dependent variable) that will be measured to determine success.
    iv. What tools and methods are to be used for collecting data.
    v. What is to be kept the same from trial to trial to ensure a fair test.
